State meter effects age
Hungry = unhappy (Boolean)
Bathroom = hungry
Full = happy
After full, time passes before bathroom



Full effects Weight
5 meals = +2 weight

Weight effects Age
4 weight = +1 age

Full effects bathroom
+5 full = +2 bathroom

Hunger effects happy
5 hungry = -3 happy

Time effects hunger
5 time = hungry

Time meter
Distance between meals effect happy meter
1 minute between meals = -1 happy
2 minutes between meals = -2 happy

Play meter
